{"word":"G87 - ἀδιάκριτος - adiákritos - ad-ee-ak'-ree-tos - Without partiality","slug":"G87","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀδιάκριτος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>adiákritos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ad-ee-ak'-ree-tos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Without partiality"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03BA;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - adiakritos</b> - <i>ad-ee-ak'-ree-tos</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G1252\">G1252</a>; properly <i>undistinguished</i>, that is, (actively) <i>impartial:</i> - without partiality."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1252\">G1252</a>, <a href=\"#/G1253\">G1253</a>, <a href=\"#/G1469\">G1469</a>, <a href=\"#/G178\">G178</a>, <a href=\"#/G2631\">G2631</a>, <a href=\"#/G2632\">G2632</a>, <a href=\"#/G2633\">G2633</a>, <a href=\"#/G2917\">G2917</a>, <a href=\"#/G2919\">G2919</a>, <a href=\"#/G2920\">G2920</a>, <a href=\"#/G2922\">G2922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2923\">G2923</a>, <a href=\"#/G2924\">G2924</a>, <a href=\"#/G350\">G350</a>, <a href=\"#/G351\">G351</a>, <a href=\"#/G470\">G470</a>, <a href=\"#/G610\">G610</a>, <a href=\"#/G611\">G611</a>, <a href=\"#/G612\">G612</a>, <a href=\"#/G843\">G843</a>"}]}